query:
CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS `goalEvidences` (
  `id` int AUTO_INCREMENT PRIMARY KEY,
  `goalId` int NOT NULL,
  `description` text NOT NULL,
  `fileUrl` varchar(500),
  `fileName` varchar(255),
  `uploadedBy` int NOT NULL,
  `createdAt` timestamp NOT NULL DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP
);
